## ðŸš€ Purpose

This repository is a professional test automation framework based on:

* Serenity BDD 4.2.22
* Screenplay Pattern
* Selenium 4.32.0
* Cucumber + Gherkin
* JUnit 4

Applied to the demo site: [AutomationPractice Demo](http://www.automationpractice.pl/index.php)

